  ministry `Ministry of Law and Justice`
  department `Department of Legal Affairs`
  longTitle `An Act to consolidate and amend the law relating to domestic arbitration, international commercial arbitration and enforcement of foreign arbitral awards as also to define the law relating to conciliation and for matters connected therewith or incidental thereto.`
